Exhaust emissions?

268
00:20:44,451 --> 00:20:48,789
Minister Park,
I almost forgot the most important part.

269
00:20:50,165 --> 00:20:52,167
If this renegotiation falls through

270
00:20:52,251 --> 00:20:55,128
and sparks a conflict
between the two nations,

271
00:20:56,004 --> 00:20:57,714
then someone

272
