and settle the matter?

335
00:26:39,639 --> 00:26:42,392
Would it be okay if he just apologized
right here, right now?

336
00:26:54,446 --> 00:26:55,822
It's between our countries.

337
00:26:57,032 --> 00:26:58,033
Mr. Lee,

338
00:26:59,284 --> 00:27:02,245
can I answer the question
you asked me earlier?

339
00:27:06,666 --> 00:27:10,211
The air pollution level test result
provided by the EPA...

340
00:27:11,713 --> 00:27:13,256
There’s an error in the numbers.

341
00:27:14,549 --> 00:27:15,675
From my calculations...

342
00:27:25,018 --> 00:27:27,479
Well, from my calculations...

343
00:27:30,774 --> 00:27:31,608
Excuse me.

344
00:27:52,754 --> 00:27:53,880
Just a second.

345
00:27:56,007 --> 00:27:57,258
Where...

346
